from fastapi import FastAPI

app = FastAPI()

@app.get("/hello/{name}")
def hello(name: str):
    return {"message": f"Hello, {name}!"}

Run: uvicorn app:app
Visit: http://localhost:8000/hello/Alice
Docs: http://localhost:8000/docs (auto-generated!)

API Key — a secret string in the header:
headers={"X-API-Key": "your-key"}

Bearer Token (JWT) — a token from logging in:
headers={"Authorization": "Bearer eyJ..."}

Never hardcode keys in source code. Use environment variables.
